
Method 1:

selections.cxx:

- make sure the ntuples with loose cuts stored in /76X/ which is in the same parent as selections.cxx:
  or you can change it in run_selections.sh

- simply run :
  source run_selections.sh

- reduced root files stored:
  ./AnalysisRegion/


Method 2:

- define your cuts in skimming.sh in the string "selection"

- simply run ./skimming.sh

- reduced root files stored in 
  ./AnalysisRegion


